---
title: Spanish One-Pot Chicken and Rice with Chorizo, Sweet Peppers, and Lemon
description: Chorizo, garlic, and red pepper give this simple one-pot recipe a Spanish twist. Cooking the chicken in the natural rendered chorizo oil gives it extra flavor and color. The best part? You’ll have enough time to clean up (or drink a glass of wine) while the rice cooks.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spanish-one-pot-chicken-and-rice-d049f545.jpg
